document_data.name: Harrowcoaster House
document_data.mainbody: '''Harrowcoaster House''' was the main office and warehouse of the [[Harrowcoaster Coster]] in [[New Velar|Harrowdale]] where fine textiles, glassware and [[spices]] were imported into the [[Dalelands]].
document_data.Locations: Harrowcoaster House was located near the shoreline on [[Moonside Lane]].
document_data.Inhabitants: The warehouse and coster were run my Captain [[Durana Shaleel]].
